# Ephemeral deployment run output — commit canonical *-latest.json pointers and
# mainnet records instead of every timestamped run snapshot.
# - hardhat = local chainId 31337 rehearsals (never useful in git)
# - launch-posture / governance-verification per-run snapshots (keep the -latest)
# - sepolia testnet timestamped deploy/launch/timelock runs
deployments/*hardhat*.json
deployments/launch-posture-*-*T*Z.json
deployments/governance-verification-*-*T*Z.json
deployments/sepolia-*T*Z.json

